---
name: styled-primitives
description: P2 styled-TkNode — status primitives (badge/tag/pill/kpiCard/tabBar), token-aware styled(), and box sizing. Lowered under default + dark themes to prove token re-resolution.
---

# Styled primitives

[lower](std/ui/lower.ssc)
[defaultTheme, darkTheme](std/ui/theme.ssc)
[badge, tag, pill, kpiCard, tabBar, styled](std/ui/display.ssc)
[box, vstack](std/ui/layout.ssc)
[text](std/ui/typography.ssc)
[Tab](std/ui/nodes.ssc)
[signal, emit](std/ui/primitives.ssc)

```scalascript
val active = signal("tab", "home")

val tree = box(maxWidth = 960)(
  vstack(8)(
    badge("Paid", "success"),
    tag("VAT", "warning"),
    pill("Overdue", "danger"),
    kpiCard("Revenue", text("$1,000")),
    tabBar(active, [Tab("#home", "Home", "home"), Tab("#tx", "Tx", "tx")]),
    styled(["bg" -> "surface", "radius" -> "md", "paddingY" -> "smd", "paddingX" -> "16"])(
      text("custom chrome")
    )
  )
)

emit(lower(tree, defaultTheme), "/tmp/ssc-styled-default")
emit(lower(tree, darkTheme), "/tmp/ssc-styled-dark")
println("styled:ok")
```
